  "events": [
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00001",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "地方上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00002",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "地方"
      ],
      "text": "惧法朝朝乐，欺公日日忧。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00003",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "地方"
      ],
      "text": "自家，西市口总甲胡斯闹便是。今日奉令旨，处决一只妖虎，一个妖僧。要把虎来剥皮示众，道是妖僧变来的。为此到市曹号令。这一桩事，委厉新奇。比往常行刑，更加严肃。这是我的干系。系大家小户所者。今日大将军亲自监斩，不是玩耍的，你们各家闭户，休连累人们。小心要紧！",
      "text_length": 127
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00004",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "地方下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00005",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00006",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "端正好",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "旧行为重抛扬，救师父同上西方。迤逦的扫除妖洞，消灾障，猛轮着金箍棒。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00007",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "俺，孙悟空。为救师父，重复下山。同了八戒先到妖精洞里略显神通。飞身来到这宝象国。好风景也！",
      "text_length": 45
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00008",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "滚绣球",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "虽然属外邦，却也山河壮。碧辉煌宫廷高敞，六市中扰扰攘攘。管弦接，按的新腔，花柳巷，扮好艳妆。不枉唤国名宝象，只可惜柏将军卖弄王章。",
      "text_length": 65
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00009",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖内鸣锣声〗。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00010",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "滚绣球",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "猛听一声锣震天响，则见那四面兵围匝地长。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00011",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "原来是妖魔诬奏将军，我师父在此典刑哩！",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00012",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "滚绣球",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "且待俺闯入法场。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00013",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空下。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00014",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众小军抬囚笼、众刽子手同上，囚笼内虎形。柏宪上，绕场。众小军分持。",
      "text_length": 33
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00015",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "刽子手，就此开刀。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00016",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众刽子手同应。孙悟空闯上，虚白。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00017",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "你是哪里来的野和尚？擅闯法场！https://scripts.xikao.com/play/020060372021-08-21左右，与我拿下！",
      "text_length": 72
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00018",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众小军同拿。孙悟空打。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00019",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "这等无礼。报名来！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00020",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "俺，休得要问俺短和长，笑你肉眼光不亮。怎便把鸱鸮做凤凰，将砥鹗加在瑚琏上。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00021",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "真凤真玉在哪里？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00022",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空指虎形。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00023",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "这不是么！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00024",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "这是真正妖魔，你怎么不是？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00025",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "你好欠明白也！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00026",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "痛周公难免流言讲，叹仲尼怎避狐裘谤。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00027",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "据你说妖魔是谁？",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00028",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "叨叨令",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "兀不是贵东床也么哥，兀不是贵东床也么哥。把妖魔反认作嫡亲半子，配着珠擎掌。",
      "text_length": 37
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00029",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "这也难相信。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00030",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "俺不与你闲讲。且救了我师父，你自明白。",
      "text_length": 19
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00031",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "孙悟空作吹气。虎形下，唐僧上。众刽子手、囚笼自两分分下。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00032",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐僧"
      ],
      "text": "徒弟，不是你来，我险些丧了命了。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00033",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "弟子救护来迟，致令师父受此魔难，皆弟子之罪也。",
      "text_length": 23
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00034",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "闻得齐天大圣孙悟空，原来就是尊驾么？",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00035",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "造化。你今认识俺孙爷爷了！我师父呵！",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00036",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "脱布衫",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "救人心反受灾殃，说法体几致危亡。不是俺前来救将，怎认出大唐朝取经三藏。",
      "text_length": 35
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00037",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "下官有眼无珠，多有得罪。大圣既能救令师返本还原，必知小女下落。",
      "text_length": 31
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00038",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "小梁州",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "俺在那黄金塔院会红妆，是君家爱女堪伤。可怜她香消粉退减容光，常把归期望，盼亲舍，泪千行。",
      "text_length": 44
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00039",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "柏宪哭。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00040",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "么篇",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "你不念亲生骨肉遭魔，一谜价蛊惑妖王。",
      "text_length": 18
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00041",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "我那儿苦煞你了！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00042",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "么篇",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "你何必假慈想，空惆怅，",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00043",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "圣僧，下官知罪了！令徒处，望乞方便。令我父女早得团圆，莫大恩德。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00044",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "唐僧"
      ],
      "text": "悟空，他的令嫒，你可救她一救。",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00045",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "师父，那百花羞呵！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00046",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "么篇",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "俺提出了天罗地网。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00047",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "几时得？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00048",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "么篇",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "顷刻里便知端详。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00049",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "猪悟能、百花羞、花香洁、闻仁同上。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00050",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "住了。请开眼。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00051",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花羞"
      ],
      "text": "这是哪里了？",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00052",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "猪悟能"
      ],
      "text": "那个不是你的父亲！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00053",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "那个不是你女儿！",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00054",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "果然是我女儿！",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00055",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "百花羞"
      ],
      "text": "爹爹！https://scripts.xikao.com/play/020060372021-08-21",
      "text_length": 52
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00056",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00057",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "此女是谁？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00058",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "这就是受冤枉闻道泉的妻子。你二人过来，见过大将军。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00059",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "下官得罪。闻娘子同小女到府中相会寒荆。闻生随下官入朝，奏明圣上。定当一力保奏，管取荣华。前者受惊，下官着实抱疚了！",
      "text_length": 57
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00060",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "车夫上，百花羞、花香洁、车夫同下。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00061",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柏宪"
      ],
      "text": "大圣，有劳神力，令我父女团圆。下官何以为报？",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00062",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "大将军！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00063",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "今朝喜得花无恙，笑杀邻家蝶自忙。乍地里团圆一堂，结果了两下悽怆。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00064",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "八戒，沙僧，随师父进朝去见国王。",
      "text_length": 16
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00065",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "煞尾",
      "speakers": [
        "孙悟空"
      ],
      "text": "俺再去剪妖狼，才不负孙爷爷重下降！",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "02006037_e00066",
      "play_id": "02006037",
      "scene_id": "02006037_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人自两边分下。https://scripts.xikao.com/play/020060372021-08-21",
      "text_length": 57
    }
  ],
  "roles_inferred": true
}